Summary: Changing scrollback size when on alternate screen clears the screen
Class: bug
Present-in: 0.56 0.59 0.60 2008-06-02
Content-type: text/x-html-body

<p>
Changing the number of lines of scrollback while in the alternate
screen causes the screen to be cleared and the cursor to be moved to
the top left. This probably shouldn't happen.
